extendedInfo.description: Do you need help finding your closest E85 fueling station? Flex-Fuel Station Locator from the Renewable Fuels Association can help! With the most up-to-date information from the Department of Energy, you'll be able to locate your closest E85 station in no time!

reviews.title: Fair
reviews.comment: While there aren\'t any good apps for flex fuel locations, this is the best I\'ve found. The tiny half-screen map area needs to be changed.
reviews.author: Rob Seelen

reviews.title: Inaccurate
reviews.comment: Horrifically out of date. Doesn\'t include over 50% of e85 stations in the Chicago area and almost 1/3 that are shown are wrong.
reviews.author: Nickolas dela Rosa

reviews.title: No good
reviews.comment: Tried using for E85 fuel and never found a station even where I knew some stations were.poor app
reviews.author: Mark Beck

reviews.title: Terrible
reviews.comment: This app doesn\'t include half the stations that sell e85 locations in the area. Some of the ones that it does show are inaccurate and the location search is confusing af! Don\'t waste your time with this app.
reviews.author: Thomas Munyer

reviews.title: JUNK
reviews.comment: This app WAS great the first week after I downloaded it, but now it won\'t even open, pops up with a message saying flex fuel has stopped working. WTF, it hasn\'t even opened yet.
reviews.author: Brigham Bailey

reviews.title: Good stuff!!!
reviews.comment: Great  just wish you could show prices
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Needs work
reviews.comment: Needs option to not show the starting point and ending point on the map, get it out of the way! Missing tons of stations
reviews.author: Jon Boettger

reviews.title: Ford2089
reviews.comment: Now its working fine.
reviews.author: Russell Dooley

reviews.title: Great app
reviews.comment: Thank you
reviews.author: Jeff Sanders

reviews.title: Does what it claims
reviews.comment: I tried this a week ago and had the force close issued too but I did the 4.0.4 update and it works great now. I uninstalled it did the update and reinstalled it and love it.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: This list is so useless
reviews.comment: Some of the stations om this list don\'t exist, and the ones I go to aren\'t on the list!  Might as well not even use this outdated info, it\'s worse than just driving around and hoping.
reviews.author: Avinash Arora

reviews.title: Junk
reviews.comment: It doesn\'t work. Don\'t waste your time.
reviews.author: Dale Scott

reviews.title: Bad App
reviews.comment: This app sucks! Almost ran out of gas because it sent me to a gas station that doesn\'t exist!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Still no update, has never worked once, crashes on startup each time ICS

reviews.comment: This app sucks! Always forced closed it never opened. Shame on myself I should have read the reviews 1st. SMH!

reviews.title: Needs prices
reviews.comment: I liked the update price feature.  It was usually pretty accurate.  If it had this, I would rate it much higher.

reviews.comment: Missing a lot of stations in my area, but a good start.
